Thomas LIDDELL, Appellant-Movant,
v.
NEW JERSEY DEPARTMENT OF CORRECTIONS, Respondent. M-690/691 September Term 2017
079493 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 9, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-690) is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-691) is denied.
